{"tid":1910723,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"一名警員遭即時停職    疑涉上周襲擊及毀壞露宿者物件","createTime":"2020-03-05T00:47:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T03:34:05.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"c3b346b0411c23a8f58c3ca577775081c6495f12","tid":1910723,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T00:47:39.000Z","msg":"一批露宿者上星期在深水埗通州街公園被警方截查，7名便衣警員被指涉嫌用鐵鎚打爛露宿者的椅子及罐頭等物品，一名女警被指涉嫌腳踩其中一名露宿者下體及扯頭髮。<br />\n<br />\n警方證實，上星期一在通州街公園進行反罪惡行動時，有警務人員涉嫌毀壞現場物件，警方高度關注，已將案件交由西九龍總區重案組進行刑事調查，一名涉及事件的警員已被即時停職。<br />\n<br />\n警方重申絕不容許警務人員有任何違法違紀行為，會公平公正、嚴肅依法跟進事件。"},{"pid":"b6c153cfb78847baf1b5eb57db493c7f7afb1ace","tid":1910723,"uid":13288,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T00:52:43.000Z","msg":"三天後復職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecfee6251fb7abd276532d494f74d06be7fb17fe","tid":1910723,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T00:58:31.000Z","msg":"Condam ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c90cb9a3073a947b3bad418aba4f8d32a1d9a3da","tid":1910723,"uid":42982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T00:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ee0d5e0d9ba8e157de880f8f70bf8a8fc714a01","tid":1910723,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T00:59:34.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7690616ebacbfe25059d9a165dbf18dd9f99e63","tid":1910723,"uid":59460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T00:59:36.000Z","msg":"訓斥下咪算囉，做咩攪咁大件事喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e8ca1931188ff0b820564ee53670c79d41e99c5","tid":1910723,"uid":